name: gqdoq
description: doq is a simple script that converts o_tree functions to q_tree functions. It expects a single input o and yield a single output o. o.query must contain the o tree function to execute. o.error contains error and o.result contains the result.

version_log.1.0.5: removed q method as it is polluting enumerations
version_log.1.0.4: added q method to object prototype
version_log.1.0.0: minor revision and out to public!
